\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>食完飯落街唱隻歌仔唔犯法架喎</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> Sing 連登靚歌 To Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四、 我相信好多區嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>街坊</strong></span>都好願意去幫和平表達意見嘅巴絲嘅，萬一流浪狗出沒再激起民憤嘅話佢哋只會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自食其果</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">公民覺醒 拯救香港</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">愛國愛港 反黑反暴</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">我哋最終嘅目標係要全民反黑反暴</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181e6f6532aaa12e8f88943ad5cfde68767e6489","tid":1416568,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c918e916a97f74a839f9e1daeafdab1b2112428","tid":1416568,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb4107099682d5251348307c4528f63caf8aa7b5","tid":1416568,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bfd77682a68d78aee282b161b5b7ae7f6c1eb23","tid":1416568,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eb9332de82dc4e8e92d6eda8ac6e0da763c8b49","tid":1416568,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src